{"tid":627465,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柔佛王儲豪氣幫全場埋單 AEON超市如「歷劫」","createTime":"2018-04-13T03:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T04:23:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7813000192a3c02c12bb10df15bab2f8d6fda2b7","tid":627465,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T03:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523520318_76db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523520318_76db.jpg&h=f029292c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180412/large/1523519285_a3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180412%2Flarge%2F1523519285_a3df.jpg&h=dc21ea79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞柔佛王儲東姑依斯邁周三前往新山一個AEON商場，期間他和王儲妃突然拿起「大聲公」宣佈，由傍晚至晚上8時，在場的每一名顧客都享有3,000令吉（約6,000港元）的免費購物額，結果即時引起哄動，超市經歷瘋搶後儼如災難現場，據稱整個活動共涉資100萬令吉（約200萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，王儲宣佈「請客」消息後便離場，現場民眾立刻高呼「吾王萬歲」，然後衝入超市內把手推車填滿。有許多後來接獲消息的民眾，都希望趕往商場分一杯羹，可惜大多數人都趕不及，要失望而回。<br />\n<br />\n在大批顧客搶購下，整間超市的貨品不用兩小時便幾乎被搶光，從照片可見，超市現場一片狼藉，凌亂的貨品四處散落，許多來不及「被埋單」的貨品被隨意遺棄在手推車上，不少貨品因此損毀白白浪費，職員無奈要善後收拾殘局。超市由於需要補貨，翌日早上要被迫暫停營業，至傍晚才能恢復營業。<br />\n<br />\n事後王儲在社交網表示，「我不是政治人物，我不需要選票，但我是真的很愛我的子民，永遠與柔州子民同在。」帖文之後獲網民廣傳，不少人要求他在當地各縣舉行同樣活動，讓所有人都可以免費購物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180413/58063577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58063577&d=0oCxB4PKUF1ZroO7ywWN2BxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=648c1a4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F58063577&h=26bee5cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180413/58063577</a>"},{"pid":"01e399c26838d475945df99836de255ab982ed17","tid":627465,"uid":6530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"個王儲叫冬菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d5d487e35d5b4c3c4c43db3730bcb172537ff8","tid":627465,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n等於買起人地成間超市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1781753c4feab6526e361f6cdb4d8fc9a0cdd29","tid":627465,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"班員工好慘, 果六千又冇份買但又要執餐死"},{"pid":"c6e4a154f8fe74e05c7c3607591380cda103e433","tid":627465,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}